## ✅ `.gitignore`

This file tells Git which files/folders to ignore. Here’s a solid default for Python + Streamlit:

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
*.log

# Virtual environments
.venv/
env/
venv/

# Streamlit
.streamlit/config.toml
.streamlit/secrets.toml

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDEs
.vscode/
.idea/
